| runtime = 30 minutes | creator = | avid editor = | sound mix = | starring = | country = Canada | network = [[Food Network (Canada)]] | first_aired = 30 August 2012 | last_aired = present | num_episodes = 66 | num_seasons = 4 | list_episodes = | website = http://www.foodnetwork.ca/ontv/shows/food-factory/show.html?titleid=282413 }}
'''''Food Factory''''' is a [[Television in Canada|Canadian]] television series produced by [[Cineflix]] airing in that country on the [[Food Network (Canada)|Food Network]], and in the [[United States]] on [[FYI (TV network)|FYI]]. The show features the industrial production lines of major food companies, mostly in Canada, but also in the United States, and occasionally in other countries.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foodnetwork.ca/ontv/shows/food-factory/show.html?titleid=282413 |title=Food Factory |accessdate=October 23, 2013}}</ref> It is co-narrated by Colleen Rusholme and Todd Schick.
